  <title>How to Argue</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>
      One could characterize a proof as arguing to the most skeptical person you have ever met that something is true.
      Now that we have our logic background, we are ready to start stringing propositions together to make these arguments. 
     
    </p>
  </introduction>

